item.title: What is Foundation Training?
item.description:
What is Foundation Training? 

You can quickly learn the tools you need to fix many of the chronic pains plaguing our daily lives. Learning to connect the Posterior Chain will teach you to move naturally, evenly absorbing the weight of your body.

item.title: PIMP MY SKIING
item.description:
PIMP MY SKIING

“Rather than treating the symptom, Pimp my skiing, reeducates your body, your brain and make you ski better”

I have used the method on severe cases of chronic pain, polio survivors, and other “incurable” conditions that doctors and other therapists have failed to treat successfully.
